   According to the children's storybook by Dr. Seuss, ``The Grinch
That Stole Christmas,'' the dour green character makes off with a
town's Christmas decorations and presents after becoming enraged by
the sounds of Christmas cheer. But the Grinch relents and returns
the booty to Whoville.
