third gang member opened fire. Alpuche, who was not a gang member,
was hit by a bullet in the chest while Christmas shopping and died
at a hospital Saturday, police said.
   Arnold refused to say which of the suspects was alleged to be the
gunman.
   In other street violence Saturday night, nine people were wounded
in five shootings. Four of those attacks were linked by police to
gangs.
