<HEAD>Lou Rawls Host of Telethon To Benefit United Negro College Fund</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Singer Lou Rawls was host of a star-studded
weekend telethon that raised more than $9.4 million in pledges for
